data.description: Active, income producing Short Term Rental!!!!Here is your chance to own an active STR in the heart of Bourbon Country. Property currently sleeps 15, but could easily be fitted up to sleep 10 more!  Home has been meticulously maintained and updated and has a 5 star ranking on Air bnb. Home has 7 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms and more character than should be allowed. For those who enjoy cooking, why not have TWO kitchens, perfect for the large gatherings! Walking distance to all downtown Frankfort has to offer and a short drive to numerous distilleries.
